<plot>It is the age of dinosaurs but the local cavemen have a few modern innovations. The anachronistic Grantite Hotel has a telephone operator who mostly wails that "nothing ever happens." The guests shower with ice-water, clad in bear-skins and bounced to their respective floors. The Dinosaur Fire Department dismantles the hotel while the telephone operator is still claiming "nothing ever happens."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?221850</url></doc>
